<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-CSW_10-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFMitchell2015" class="citation news cs1"><a href="/wiki/Austin_Mitchell" title="Austin Mitchell">Mitchell, Austin</a> (4 June 2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.civilserviceworld.com/articles/review/meddle-management-review-%E2%80%98-government-worked-better-and-cost-less%E2%80%99">"Meddle management: A review of 'A Government that Worked Better and Cost Less?'<span class="cs1-kern-right"></span>"</a>. <i>Civil Service World</i>. London: <a href="/wiki/Dod%27s_Parliamentary_Communications" class="mw-redirect" title="Dod's Parliamentary Communications">Dod's Parliamentary Communications</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Civil+Service+World&amp;rft.atitle=Meddle+management%3A+A+review+of+%27A+Government+that+Worked+Better+and+Cost+Less%3F%27&amp;rft.date=2015-06-04&amp;rft.aulast=Mitchell&amp;rft.aufirst=Austin&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.civilserviceworld.com%2Farticles%2Freview%2Fmeddle-management-review-%25E2%2580%2598-government-worked-better-and-cost-less%25E2%2580%2599&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AA+Government+that+Worked+Better+and+Cost+Less%3F" class="Z3988"></span></span>
