<li id="cite_note-TP-11">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-TP_11-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
